Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:57.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}その量子がもつれ合えば　ゼロになる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:03.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is no god.　Wonderful new world.
