Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}召唤着我们伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:36.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}也许能回忆起
